==English==
===Noun===
'''demon''' ([[demons]])

# an [[evil]] [[spirit]]
# the [[devil]]; [[Satan]]; [[Lucifer]]; the Light-Bearer
# any of the [[fallen angel]]s who serve Satan
# a [[foible]]; a [[flaw]] in a person's [[character]]
: ''The demon of [[stupidity]] [[haunt]]s me whenever I open my mouth.''

